{"lastModified":1766395996169,"uri":"c::7579684728::vessel::77940a01-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nThe main deck of Alibaba creates a seamless connection between the interior  and exterior, inviting guests to experience life at sea in effortless harmony. The spacious layout is designed for maximum enjoyment, whether relaxing in the sun, hosting friends, or taking in the stunning views. From the open flybridge, where panoramic vistas await, to the inviting salon that exudes warmth and sophistication, Alibaba offers a luxurious setting for complete freedom and unforgettable moments on the water.\n\nGuest Accommodation\nBuilt in 2022, Alibaba offers luxurious accommodation for up to 6 guests in 3 cabins: a master suite, a VIP double cabin, and a twin cabin. The yacht has 3 guest toilets and 1 toilet in the skipper's cabin.\nIt can also accommodate up to 2 crew members, ensuring a relaxed and personalized yacht charter experience.\n\nOnboard Comfort & Entertainment\nAlibaba offers premium features for comfort and entertainment, including Wi-Fi connectivity for guests who wish to stay connected. The yacht is equipped with air conditioning, a surround sound system and a fully equipped galley. The spacious salon and hard top provide ample protection from the sun while allowing guests to enjoy all the amenities onboard.\n\nPerformance & Range\nAlibaba is powered by Volvo Penta D13-900 engines, offering smooth cruising and excellent fuel efficiency.","blueprint":{"name":"ALIBABA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a01-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::74928f90-3624-11f0-91c8-cf9e8412c7bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a01-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::74917e20-3624-11f0-91c8-cf9e8412c7bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a01-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::74932bd0-3624-11f0-91c8-cf9e8412c7bd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77